{
 "file": "_STG08SP.bin",
 "source_size": 29000,
 "built_size": 31491,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14e6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和平者队、已突破博亚兹的防卫线！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e887ef6ee7c902ef3ae8b6ef6dec4de7d6e856e7b4e968e9b2e916ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x151b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "死亡军团、开始向雅金·杜维进军！！",
   "zh_hex": "15a7ebb2e7e0ea5e02e7fae9089debfde90204e8cbea54e892e7e0060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1556",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈哈哈哈、太精彩了！不愧是未来的科技{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7e8e7e8e7e802e86ae98ded58e7baef97e7b5ea08e7b6e8b4efcfe7b4ebe3ea6400ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x156d",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要有了这份数据、调整者那帮家伙、转{00}眼就能全灭。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7cbe7bae7b9ea22e914e8cc02e95ce9feef6ee7b7e910e7dfe7fd02e9c200e90be7c5e7c6efb4e8e1030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c7",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀？怎么了、特列斯上级特佐？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c605e7f2e7bde7ba02e7cfe8b5e7c8ef4ceaeee7cfefba050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15db",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莫非、有什么不满吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15eba0e8f002e7cbe7dde7bde7b5eb61e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1604",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不满……是啊、若说我对眼前这一幕有所{00}感触、那确实可以这么说。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5eb610909e7b6e7c302e7e7e7edefcce7bee90bef51e7b9efb6ec14e7cbe7fb00e87def4802e7b7e88ce87fe7c4e7f3e7b9e7bde7ed030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x162b",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对这种不配称作战斗的武力、我们OZ、{00}根本无需特地出手相助……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7b9e7d1e7b5ea34ea01ef2fef28e7ffe7b4e8ecefb002efcce7bbed1ceeda0200e9b8efa6e7dce92de7cfef63efbeef66e8b1ea2309090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164d",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们就为下一场战斗做准备、在后方静观{00}其变吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7c5e7c1ef4defb6e876ef28e7ffe81ce87ae87702ef29e7feefb1eab3eaf200e8cfe955e7d003000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16d2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……真没办法。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e820e7d8e8eae84e030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16db",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这种打法、看来是不合他的口味啊。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e7d1e7f5e84e02e7f6efcfe7b6e7b5efc0e80ce7b4eabded36e7c3030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16f8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、随他去吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e9a1e80ce7ebe7d003000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1703",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正本来就打算、等灭了PLANT之后、再{00}借用OZ的战力。",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3bd2d9e7c5e7f5e88902e826e8e1e7baeed4e024ea9ceed3eed6e7cde7fe02e80b00eadcd8ed1ceedae7b4ef28da0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1726",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……来、舰长、也该去做最后的收尾了。",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcf02e7d4ef3402e7c0e898e7ebe81ce8c5e7fee7b4e926ebc0e7ba0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1759",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "收尾……吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e926ebc00909e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x177f",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这还用问吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7f7efb3e997e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x178c",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "把PLANT……摧毁掉啊。",
   "zh_hex": "15e81beed4e024ea9ceed3eed60909efe5e97ce9d3e7c3030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b3",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎夫特的MS部队、正在展开！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be830e7cfe7b4efa7ef9eef70e7c902ef3bef29e989e7faef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17f2",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的……不过是垂死挣扎罢了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b40909e7b5ef36e7b6ed41ef6aebcae84beaefe7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1823",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……所以呢、各位！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7fbe7f3e90702e819e834ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1834",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "核导弹打过去时、它们碍事得很、就请把{00}扎夫特的MS都清除掉吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f3ea4be946e7f5ef36e7ebef2d02e978e7bbe8c6efb8e80ae98102e7c5e83ae81b00e84be830e7cfe7b4efa7ef9ee840e995e974e9d3e7d003000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18a2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "捷利特……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bce82ee7cf09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c4",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、我知道……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3028be85ae82a0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18d2",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没有那帮家伙的支援、提坦斯就维持不下{00}去、这道理我懂。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7cbe7b7e910e7dfe7fde7b4e883e86302e821e843e7c8e7c5ea54e9efe7b58900e7eb02e7b9e82ae8728be8b003000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ef",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽是叫人不痛快的命令、可也只能服从、{00}是吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7b6e8c1efb2e7b5ea0be85fe7b4e853e94e02e7c4e7c0ef32e7c6e9f1e88a0200e7b6e7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1932",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……主天使号、{00}攻击阵位、已经布置完毕",
   "zh_hex": "150909e954e844e83fe83302009ee7cceb48e83402ef3ae8b7e831ea0ee87eea2c00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1964",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就开始吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e7fae908e7d0030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19b8",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀、怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c602e7f2e7bde7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c2",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难不成、连你也对这场战斗看不顺眼吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e7b5e83702e86ee7b8e7c0e7bee7b9e876ef28e7ffe7f6e7b5eab4e90be7d0050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19ff",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……这场战斗、确实是会结束的。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e88ce87fe7b6e7e2e868e895e7b403000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a17",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……以彻底消灭敌人的方式。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f3ebc5e9b4e928e8e1e7e3efb2e7b4efb1ea260300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a42",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就毫无问题了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5ea0ae7dce997ea12e7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a54",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "攻击、就请开始吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef67e7cc02e7c5e83ae7fae908e7d003000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a88",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c602e7b7e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab8",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我以统御月球与地球的女王之名、向两军{00}下令！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f3e929ec68e850efd3e832ef63efd3e7b4efade884e7cde8ac02efc1e97de7e000ef4de94eef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ad2",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "立即停止战斗、即刻撤出这片宙域！",
   "zh_hex": "15e86be855e934e869ef28e7ff02e855e91fe90aefbee7b9ee5ee8bfeaa7ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b13",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真没想到、迪安娜女王竟会插手这场战斗{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7d8e7e6e7d702ea11e7fce7eaefade884ef2ce7e2eb08ef66e7b9e876ef28e7ff000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b2f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今才跳出来、真不知她在打什么主{00}意。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb9e836edbbefbeefcf02e820e7b5e85ae88eef29e7f5e7dde7bde95400ef3c03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b68",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔先生……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b8f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种货色、不去理会就是、反正她也成不{00}了什么气候。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1eaf5e89f02e7b5e7ebe872e7e2e7c5e7b602e87cef3be88ee7c0e837e7b500e7bae7dde7bde8edea3903000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bca",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可是迪安娜女王、是受地球联邦委托{00}执掌统治的人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7b6ea11e7fce7eaefade88402e7b6e8c8ef63efd3ef2eefaaee08e7f400e9fceb36e929ea79e7b4efb209090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c06",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那也几乎只是个空有的名头罢了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c0eaa5e933ef32e7b6e828e93fe7cbe7b4e8ace92eeaefe7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c1c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你看、如今打得这么热闹、她也只能带来{00}那么点兵力。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f602e7f0efb9e7f5e80ae7b9e7bdead1ead802e88ee7c0ef32e7c6e937efcf00e7b7e7bde822ef93efb00300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c3e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明月之民、早就对地球失去了影响力、",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e850e7cdef3802e963e7c5e7beef63efd3e8a5e7ebe7baea8eecbfefb00200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5f",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那位女王陛下、却偏偏不明白这一点。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e834efade884eb24ef4d02eadfeb4deb4de7b5ef39e809e7b9efb6e8220300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c72",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "肯就这么回去倒也罢了……若要碍事、那{00}就当作敌人清除便是。",
   "zh_hex": "15e93de7c5e7b9e7bdef52e7ebe848e7c0eaefe7ba0909e7e7ef2ae8c6efb802e7b700e7c5ef53ef2fe7e3efb2e995e974e8fae7b603000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cae",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜女王、是敌人……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7eaefade88402e7b6e7e3efb20909ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cd7",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说到底、那群月之民、终究是宇宙那一边{00}的人……也就是、地球的敌人。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede7d7e9b402e7b7ecfae850e7cdef3802e8e2e906e7b6e8bee8bfe7b7efb6e89900e7b4efb20909e7c0e7c5e7b602ef63efd3e7b4e7e3efb20300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cf8",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人就必须消灭、不是吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7c5e860e9a2e928e8e102e7b5e7b6e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d59",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "迪安娜大人！再继续停留下去、太危险了{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2ef97e80be9d6e9ade934e98cef4de7eb02e86ae935e932e7ba00ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da6",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是我力有不及……真是不甘心。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efccefb0e7cbe7b5e9cf0909e820e7b6e7b5ecede82d03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1de7",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你们这些家伙！这分明就是叛逆之举{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b8e7bbe7b9e8a4e7dfe7fdef97e7b9efaeef39e7c5e7b6ef43eeb4e7cdea2100090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e17",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇啊啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea88e7c3e7c3e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e99",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和平者队的镇压、已经完成八成左右。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e887ef6ee7c9e7b4eebde99202ef3ae8b7e87ee837ecafe837ec65ec500300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ece",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "辛苦了、蕾蒂、就这样继续进行下去吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15ea58e9e6e7ba02e84ce9f502e7c5e7b9e7dae9d6e9ade892efd6ef4de7ebe7d003000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1efc",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f26",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从不带来痛苦的战斗中、人是什么也学不{00}到的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ae7b5e937efcfea0be9e6e7b4ef28e7ffef4e02efb2e7b6e7dde7bde7c0eb55e7b500e7d7e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f48",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "放马过来吧、穆尔塔·阿兹拉埃尔。",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ce84fef36efcfe7d002eb10e7e1e945ef4be7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e103000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f56",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我要让你……不、要让所有卷入这场战争{00}的人……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef2ae7f9e7b80909e7b502ef2ae7f9e7fbe7cbecbae891e7b9e876ef28e85200e7b4efb2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f74",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……都领会到、战争的悲惨。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e840ea20e7e2e7d702ef28e852e7b4e9dfed5d030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙、到底在想些什么啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4ef29e7e6e8a4e7dde7bde7c3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1faf",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明明再加把劲、这场战争就要赢了啊！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39ef39e80be854e81beb5002e7b9e876ef28e852e7c5ef2ae9cbe7bae7c3ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fcb",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可那家伙竟然……！！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b7e7dfe7fdef2ce7ef0909ef97ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ff5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请您、务必冷静下来、阿兹拉埃尔先生。",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae83502e94fe860eb4eeab3ef4defcf02e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8d03000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x200a",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "眼下该考虑的、是如何应对这一局面。",
   "zh_hex": "15e90bef4de898eb41eba1e7b402e7b6e7f0efbce873e7bee7b9efb6ea8ce86203000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2049",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这种事我当然懂！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e7d1efb8efccef53e7efe8b0ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2077",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、接下来打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702efceef4defcfe7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2084",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再跟扎夫特打下去、是不可能了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be973e84be830e7cfe7f5ef4de7eb02e7b6e7b5e7c4e7c6e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20b5",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那种事、不是明摆着的吗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7d1efb802e7b5e7b6ef39eb8be86de7b4e802ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20c9",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们要去讨伐发动叛乱的特列斯！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbef2ae7ebe9f7eb26e870ef30ef43e976e7b4e7cfe8b5e7c8ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ed",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长！总之、先把我们手头的战力集结起{00}来！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef3406e881e7cd02b8e81b8be7bbaee92ee7b4ef28daea98e868e84700d9060000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x210d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "集结一完成、就镇压那帮叛逆者！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea98e86887e87ee83702e7c5eebde992e7b7e910ef43eeb4ad0600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2140",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明白了。",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef39e809e7ba030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2184",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你这样、真的好吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b9e7da02e820e7b4e7c7e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21af",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……？你指的是什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15090905e7b8e8c0e7b4e7b6e7dde7bd05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21d8",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是说、就这样一直听那个叫阿兹拉埃尔{00}的家伙的、真的好吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7ed02e7c5e7b9e7daefb6e875e8d1e7b7e828e8c1e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e100e7b4e7dfe7fde7b402e820e7b4e7c7e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x220d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我接到军本部的命令、要服从阿兹拉埃尔{00}先生的指示。",
   "zh_hex": "15efccefcee7d7e7e0efa6ef70e7b4e853e94e02ef2ae9f1e88ae7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e100ef8bef8de7b4e8c0eab003000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2248",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我问的不是那套场面话、是你心里到底怎{00}么想的。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce997e7b4e7b5e7b6e7b7eb30e876e862e81f02e7b6e7b8e82def31e7d7e9b4e7f200e7bde7e6e7b4030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22a3",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "服从军令固然没错、可一旦过了头、是不{00}会有好下场的。",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f1e88ae7e0e94eeac0e7efe7d8e88502e7c4efb6ebcdef36e7bae92e02e7b6e7b500e7e2e7cbe7c7ef4de876e7b40300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e2",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "服从命令、是身为军人的本分！哪还有个{00}人判断的余地……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f1e88ae853e94e02e7b6e88de7c1e7e0efb2e7b4efa6efaeef97e8ffe7f7e7cbe82800efb2eb29e982e7b4eb27ef630909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2323",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、只要有命令、你连军人以外的人、{00}也照样举枪相向吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef32ef2ae7cbe853e94e02e7b8e86ee7e0efb2e7f3e8f7e7b4efb20200e7c0ea1ae7daea21eaaee8b1efc1e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x235e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2383",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我以前、也曾经那样做过。",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7f3ef5102e7c0ea2ae8b7e7b7e7dae81cef36030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ae",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d0",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我遵照上头的命令、对SIDE2发动了{00}攻击……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccec40ea1aef4ce92ee7b4e853e94e02e7beef9eef62ef96ef9fef5fe870ef30e7ba00ef67e7cc0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ea",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "结果、整座殖民地的居民、都被我的部队{00}斩尽杀绝了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e868e87102e9feebc4e8a9ef38ef63e7b4ea4cef3802e840e7f1efcce7b4ef70e7c900ed71e8f2e89be91ce7ba030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2426",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x244b",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没错。一周战争……就是吉翁毁灭三座殖{00}民地的那场战争。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e8850387ea5cef28e8520909e7c5e7b6e7d9ee88e97ce8e1eaa0ebc4e8a900ef38bfe7b4e7b7e876ef28e85203000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x246b",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而我所率领的海兵队、正是那场大屠杀的{00}急先锋。",
   "zh_hex": "15e89cefcce7fbe9e1ea20e7b4e91bef93e7c902ef3be7b6e7b7e876efa5ed4fe89be7b400ea62ef8be967030000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x248b",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也因此遭到友军的轻视……回过神来、已{00}是无处可去……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0ef33e7caeb1ee7d7e960e7e0e7b4e990e9d909098cef36e9aad902ef3a00e7b6e7dce903e7c4e7eb090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24ae",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……事到如今再怎么后悔、也早就无力回{00}天了。",
   "zh_hex": "150909efb8e7d7e7f0efb9e80be7f2e7bde7feeb8602e7c0e963e7c5e7dcefb0ef5200e844e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24e3",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西玛·卡拉豪……您……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e845ef4be801e7c2eea20909e8350909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x250e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、你也该多少动动自己的脑袋了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b8e7c0e898e7e9efacef30ef30efb5e8c9e7b4eb67ed04e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25e7",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格……你要走吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e8240909e7b8ef2ae890e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x260d",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2614",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不能就这样、放着瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利{00}不管。",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b5e7c6e7c5e7b9e7da02e86ce86de8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e00e7b5e93b0300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2649",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、那个人她……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7b7e828efb2e88e090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2694",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你是打算、再重犯一次和从前一样的{00}错误吗、西格·韦德纳？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7b6e7f5e88902e80be8a1eb0eefb6e864e7d3e88aef51efb6e7dae7b400e885ea33e80202e7f8e824ef4bebaee82ce88205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26cd",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "克瓦特罗大尉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d5e99fe7cfe7ecefa5efc6090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26f1",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你被私情所困、是不是已经看不清、自己{00}真正该做的事了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7f1efd5e88be7fbeaff02e7b6e7b5e7b6ef3ae8b7e7f6e7b5e99502efb5e8c900e820ef3be898e81ce7b4efb8e7ba050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2738",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "私情……或许吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15efd5e88b0909e905e8a7e7d0030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2760",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e8240909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2784",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但即便如此、我也无所谓。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe855e8fae7f0e7ca02efcce7c0e7dce7fbe92b03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2795",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "亲眼送走他最后一程的、是我、是我亲手{00}把他……",
   "zh_hex": "15e894e90be9bae890e80ce8c5e7feefb6ea7de7b402e7b6efcc02e7b6efcce894ef6600e81be80c0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27b4",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以这一次、也要由我亲手……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f3e7b9efb6e86402e7c0ef2ae8a6efcce894ef660909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27df",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕那对谁而言、都是无法获得救赎的结{00}局？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958e7b7e7bee923e89cefd702e840e7b6e7dce84ee9d8e80ae8caeff1e7b4e86800ea8c0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2814",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我从没想过要被救赎、只是、想做个了断{00}罢了……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce88ae7d8e7e6ef36ef2ae7f1e8caeff102ef32e7b602e7e6e81ce828e7bae98200eaefe7ba09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2836",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与那段过去的一切、{00}做个彻底的了断",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832e7b7ea6bef36e7ebe7b487ef3f0200e81ce828ebc5e9b4e7b4e7bae982000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28bf",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西格……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e82409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2901",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟蕾因·伊克斯贝利……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae84cef3304e969e7d5e7c8e857e82e0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x290b",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、要将你……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02ef2ae84ae7b80909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x292f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……瑟拉。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8aae7c2030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2959",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2970",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x299a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是谁……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e923090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29b6",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我那可爱的人偶……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b7e7c4e8d5e7b4efb2ea850909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ef",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你才是真正的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e836e7b6e820ef3be7b409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ff",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "瑟拉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8aae7c2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a32",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、是瑟蕾因！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7b6e8aae84cef33ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a3c",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么瑟拉、我根本不认识！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bde8aae7c202efcce9b8efa6e7b5e8a0e92fef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aad",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我爱你……瑟拉。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8d5e7b80909e8aae7c2030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ad4",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手！我……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66ef97efcc0909ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b28",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b38",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b3e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是梦……吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ea400909e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bce",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我爱你……瑟拉。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8d5e7b80909e8aae7c2030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c2e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个男人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828ea95efb20909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c37",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他、唤我作瑟拉……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80c02ec0eefccef2fe8aae7c20909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c66",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嚯……竟把迪安娜的∀高达给反杀了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dd0909ef2ce81bea11e7fce7eae7b4effee812ef2be839e87ce89be7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c81",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那艘战舰、记得是叫主天使号吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7eb18ef28e7d402e996e80ae7b6e8c1e954e844e83fe833e7d005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cb0",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cd2",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本以为地球人没什么像样的战力、没想到{00}、还真有点门道……",
   "zh_hex": "15d2e7f3e7c1bf95b4e7d8e7dde7bde8e9e7dae7b4ef28da02e7d8e7e6e7d70002e7f7e820e7cbe822e90ce82a0909000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d10",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、基姆……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e829e8230909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d37",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本想等局势再变动些、再采取行动、不过{00}、计划有变！",
   "zh_hex": "15efa6e7e6e826ea8ce8fde80be955ef30e8a402e80bec9ee987efd6ef3002e7b5ef360002ea55ea74e7cbe955ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d67",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "梅丽贝尔！把倒X准备好！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9f2e9c5e857e7e1ef97e81be848eed9e87ae877e7c7ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d7b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们金卡拉姆舰队、终于、到了登上历史{00}舞台的时候了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe902e801e7c2e823e7d4e7c902e8e2e87902e7d7e7bae9a0ef4ce8fbe92500eb9eea16e7b4ef2dea39e7baef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dac",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔理事！再继续留在这里、太危{00}险了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1e872efb8ef97e80be9d6e9ade98cef29e7b9ef3102e86ae93500e932e7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2de6",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "扎夫特那些人、也挺有两下子的嘛。",
   "zh_hex": "15e84be830e7cfe7b7e8a4efb202e7c0eb5ce7cbe97def4de886e7b4e9360300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2df9",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、那也没办法、就请先后撤吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b7e7c0e7d8e8eae84e02e7c5e83aef8be7fee90ae7d003000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e11",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "余下的、就交给巴基露露舰长去处理吧。",
   "zh_hex": "15eb27ef4de7b402e7c5e861e839e85be829e858e858e7d4ef34e7ebe903e872e7d0030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6756",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！竟会在这种地方……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ef2ce7e2ef29e7b9e7d1ef63efb10909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6796",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方部队、已清除完毕！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1ef70e7c902ef3ae995e974e87eea2cef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67cf",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了、那么、也该把那个碍眼的沙漏给砸{00}个粉碎了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7ba02e7b7e7bd02e7c0e898e81be7b7e828e8c6e90be7b4eb0cece9e839efec00e828ee7debe0e7ba030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x67f0",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "让和平者队、向前推进……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f9e7d3e887ade7c9029dbaeaabe892090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x683a",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿、阿兹拉埃尔理事！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d202e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1e872efb8ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6860",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、慌成这副样子？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02eb05e837e7b9ecb6e7dae886050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x688c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "OZ、OZ它……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1ceeda02ed1ceedae9780909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6898",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原本在后方待命的OZ军、向和平者队发{00}起了攻击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e4efa6ef29e7feefb1eaa8e853e7b4ed1ceedae7e002efc1e7d3e887ef6ee7c9e87000e847e7baef67e7ccef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x68d0",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7dde7bdef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6902",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哎呀！真是干得漂亮、舰长！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dce9c6ef97e820e7b6e8d3e80aead0eaa202e7d4ef34ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6933",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔先生……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1ef8bef8d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x695a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这下碍事的家伙也清除掉了、差不多、该{00}来收拾它了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef4de8c6efb8e7b4e7dfe7fde7c0e995e974e9d3e7ba02e9c7e7b5e7e902e89800efcfe926eae6e978e7ba090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x697b",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……收拾掉那个碍眼的沙漏。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e926eae6e9d3e7b7e828e8c6e90be7b4eb0cece9030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6989",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和平者队、向前推……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e887ade7c9029dbaeaab090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69c2",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "发射准备就绪！",
   "zh_hex": "15e870ef65e87ae877e7c5efeeef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x69e7",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好——！全弹、一齐发射！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ebafebafef97efb4e94602efb6e924e870ef65ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a1e",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "核、核弹！？可恶、你们这帮自然人！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f302e8f3e946ef9705e7c4e7de02e7b8e7bbe7b9e910efb5e7efefb2ef97ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a4e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可、可恶、这帮家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c402e7c4e7de02e7b9e910e7dfe7fdef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a5c",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "打倒一个又冒出一个、根本没完！！这到{00}底有多少架……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f5e848efb6e828e8f1eb7fefbeefb6e82802e9b8efa6e7d8e87eef97ef97e7b9e7d700e9b4e7cbe7e9eface99d0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6a9e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队、队长……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c902e7c9ef3409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ada",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哇啊啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea88e7c3e7c3e7c3ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b82",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路征战至今、辛苦你了。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ecd2ef28e897efb902ea58e9e6e7b8e7ba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6b8f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "衷心感谢你、将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一{00}路玩到了最后。",
   "zh_hex": "15edb3e82de87de8b2e7b802e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb600e8d2e970e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6baf",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就此暂告一{00}段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5e7cae9ffe8e5efb600ea6be92a090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bce",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、往后也愿你尽情游{00}玩下去。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8f2e88bea9400e970ef4de7eb0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6bf3",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "此外、为通关本路线的你、还准备了一个{00}特别关卡。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cae8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7baefb6e82800e7cfe7e5e8bbe801030000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c1a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那便是与另行作战至今的大天使队进行的{00}特别演习。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8fae7b6e832e99befd6ef2fef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd6e7b400e7cfe7e5ea2feab603000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c3b",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}究竟有多强、也未尝不可。",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e906ef2ce7cbe7e9e8ad02e7c0e8b4eccfe7b5e7c403000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c60",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bbefb6e8abe812ef4d0300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6c85",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6ca9",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你慢慢品味、尽兴玩到最后。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e979e979eae1ed3602e8f2eabae970e7d7e8c5e7fe030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d22",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路走来、能陪着我这样不可靠的舰长、{00}真是谢谢你。",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2e890efcf02e7c6ef42e86defcce7b9e7dae7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef340200e820e7b6e8b2e8b2e7b8030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d41",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条「平成高达路线」、{00}就到此告一段落了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d4e9c3e887e837e812ef2be8d2e916e9c40200e7c5e7d7e7cae8e587ea6be92ae7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d5f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们预防者的战斗已经结束…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e8950900090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d79",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……游戏本身也还能继续玩下去哦、往后{00}也请尽情享受游戏吧。",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea94ea3eefa6e88de7c0e7f7e7c6e9d6e9ade970ef4de7ebe91902e911e7fe00e7c0e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c8ea94ea3ee7d0030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6d9f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩到最后的你、我们也准备了全新{00}的关卡哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802efcce7bbe7c0e87ae877e7baefb4ef8a00e7b4e8bbe801e91903000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dc3",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头作战、一直在和提坦斯、{00}新吉翁交手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92eef2fef280287e875ef29e7d3e821e843e7c80200ef8ae7d9ee88e861aee7b4090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6dde",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦。",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e919030000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6df1",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战了哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef28e7bae9190300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e17",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请你、也务必来挑战一下哦。",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7b802e7c0e94fe860efcfeae7ef28efb6ef4de91903000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e25",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6e49",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『燃起对战的战火！全速冲锋吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150ceb93e847e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97efb4e9dae95ee967e7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6eca",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露中{00}佐。",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e858ef4e00efba03000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6eda",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}、致以敬意。",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e9490002ea32e7f3ee38ef3c030000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6efc",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的全力协助、我们才终于得以一{00}战到底。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4efb4efb0e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3efb600ef28e7d7e9b4030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f1e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、到此就结束了。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7d7e7cae7c5e868e895e7ba0300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f34",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽说我们主天使队的战斗已经告终{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7edefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e8e5e8e2000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f4d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、往后也愿你尽情游{00}玩下去。",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e911e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8f2e88bea9400e970ef4de7eb030000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f71",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、此外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cae8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6f9c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、{00}预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82c04e857e7e10200ea5ae968ade8929fef2ea0ea2feab600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fba",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的本事、与他们一战、也定{00}能取得胜利。",
   "zh_hex": "158be8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4d2a902e832e80ce7bb87ef2802e7c0e86700e7c6e987e80ae8dbe82e0300000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x6fdf",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请尽情享受『SD高达G{00}世代DS』、",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae8f2e88bec06e8c80c1411e812ef2beed100e83ce8e711140d0200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7003",
   "jp_len": 16,
